name: Spraypaint of Planet Earth - Galactibles™ #23
description: Holy Krylon! Congratulations, you’ve discovered Galactible™ #23, the “Spraypaint of Planet Earth!” The invention of spraypaint on planet Earth transformed its landscape into a colorful gallery and spearheaded the greatest artistic revolution known as "Graffiti." This artistic renaissance, the largest on Planet Earth, lead to the uprising of the underground and downfall of the tyrannical overlords, culminating with the battle of 2076. Snatch this Galactible quick and wield the power of spraypaint! Mark your name wherever you go, ward away evil-doers, and communicate with others through cryptic symbols! Your Mana has been raised by +4,444,000 bits! Custom music made by Pyramid Guy. Galactibles™ are one-of-a-kind and minted as 1-of-1. Only 99 will be made! New Galactibles™ drop every week (sorta) on twitter, so give us a follow @Galactibles! Certified authentic and original animations made by Pyramid Guy (IG: @pyramidguy), aka Kris Kanaly (TW: @kriskanaly). Galactibles™ ©2021 | galactibles.com
